    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint condition and represents a rare find for a discerning buyer. The exterior paint is flawless, with no chips, scratches, or dings, and it retains its original factory showroom shine. Inside, the leather upholstery is supple and shows virtually no signs of wear, while the dashboard and all interior trim pieces are in perfect state. Mechanically, the car performs exceptionally well; the engine is quiet and powerful, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and all electronic components work exactly as they should. It has been meticulously maintained with a full service history and has always been stored in a climate-controlled garage. This is an immaculate example that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
