    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence, this vehicle is in showroom condition and has been meticulously maintained since day one. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with a professional ceramic coating, showing no swirls, chips, or imperfections. It has been strictly garage-kept and never driven in inclement weather. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats still retain their factory-fresh scent and show zero signs of wear or bolster compression. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assistance suite, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. The engine bay is immaculate, and the performance is as sharp as the day it rolled off the assembly line. Fitted with brand-new high-performance tires and unmarked alloy wheels, this car is ready for the most discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
